Brazilian footballer, Neymar, and his lover, Bruna Biancardi, are expecting their first child. Sharing the news on his Instagram page Neymar wrote, “We dream of your life, we plan your arrival and know that you are here to complete our love, leave our days much happier. “You’re going to join a beautiful family, with a brother, grandparents, uncles, and aunts who already love you very much! “Come soon child, we are waiting for you! “ ‘Before I formed you in the womb I chose you; before you were born I set you apart’ – Jeremiah 1:5.”